snippet.title: A relaxing, casual idle game! | Dungeon Vending Machines Demo Release
snippet.description:
Dungeon Vending Machines is a relaxing, casual idle game where you run vending machines in a dungeon! As adventurers face the dangerous depths, you’ll be their lifeline. Expand your machine lineup, grow your profits, and become the ultimate dungeon supplier!

Steam ➜ https://store.steampowered.com/app/3317780
